					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One idea I had but didn't know how well it would have bode is when you press select, you would activate the "bionic boots" (... kept the bionic commando theme in mind). When the boots are activated, the colors of the boots changes to tell the user that you're now in jump mode.  In that mode, you can use the bionic arm and jump.  If you need more precision, you just deactivate the boots.
<br />
<br />It all depends how you would use the arm in the end thought.</div>

